
REQUIRED Packages:

   Python 2.6 or 2.7
   Numpy 1.3.0 or later
   SAMPy 1.1 or later
   Sherpa 4.3
   

INSTALL sherpa_samp-0.1:

   python setup.py install --prefix=<install dir>


TEST

Start the SAMP hub in a terminal window

% <install dir>/bin/sampy


Start the sherpa_samp server in a terminal window

% <install dir>/bin/sherpa_samp


Run the sherpa_samp client in a terminal window

% cd <source dir>/examples
% python -i samp_send.py --file 3c273.txt


